objects.description: [TA505](https://attack.mitre.org/groups/G0092) has used lures to get users to click links in emails and attachments, enable content in malicious attachments, and execute malicious files contained in archives. For example, [TA505](https://attack.mitre.org/groups/G0092) makes their malware look like legitimate Microsoft Word documents, .pdf and/or .lnk files.
